car.viewer.client
Class Car

java.lang.Object
  car.viewer.client.Car

public class Car
extends java.lang.Object

Represents a car--with location, rotation, and scale--to be drawn onto a CarViewer. Exports a native JavaScript interface class Car when statically initialized, or when export() is called.

Author:
Joshua Little
